Package de.akquinet.jbosscc.guttenbase.export

Interface Summary
ExportDumpExtraInformation Give the user a possibility to add extra informations to the dumped data.
Exporter Export schema information and table data to some custom format.
ExporterFactory Create @see Exporter for dumping database using @see ExportDumpConnector.
ExportTableHeader Denote start of new table in export file.
ImportDumpExtraInformation Give the user a possibility to retrieve extra informations from the dumped data.
Importer Import schema information and table data from some custom format.
ImporterFactory Create @see Importer for reading dumped database using @see ImportDumpConnector.

ExportDumpBlob Since BLOBs may be quite big.

ExportDumpDatabaseConfiguration Export dump configuration forwards important events to ExportDumpConnection.
ExportDumpPreparedStatement Custom implementation of PreparedStatement dumping data to the given output stream.
ExportTableHeaderImpl Denote start of new table in export file
ImportDumpConnection Special "Connection" that supports reading data from a stream.
ImportDumpConnectionInfo Connection info for importing data from a file.
ImportDumpConnector Connection info for importing data from a file.
ImportDumpDatabaseConfiguration Import dump configuration forwards important events to ImportDumpConnection.
ImportDumpPreparedStatement Custom implementation of PreparedStatement reading data from the given input stream.
ImportDumpResultSet Special ResultSet that reads data from the given stream.
